Usage: codd [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...

  CoDD: Coherence-Driven Development.

Options:
  --version  Show the version and exit.
  --help     Show this message and exit.

Commands:
  assemble      Assemble generated sprint fragments into a working project.
  audit         Change review pack — validate + impact + policy + review...
  extract       Extract design documents from existing codebase...
  fix           Fix test/build failures using AI guided by design documents.
  generate      Generate CoDD documents for a specific wave.
  hooks         Manage Git hook integration.
  impact        Analyze change impact from git diff.
  implement     Generate implementation code from the implementation plan.
  init          Initialize CoDD in a project directory.
  mcp-server    Start MCP server for AI tool integration (stdio).
  measure       Show project metrics — graph health, coverage, quality,...
  plan          Show wave execution status from configured artifacts.
  policy        Check source code against enterprise policy rules.
  propagate     Propagate source code changes to design documents.
  repair-slice  Generate compact repair context for located files (patch...
  require       Infer requirements from extracted codebase facts...
  restore       Restore design documents from extracted codebase facts...
  review        Review design documents for content quality using AI.
  risk          Analyze change risk using the codd-pro extension pack.
  scan          Scan codebase and update dependency graph (Stage 1).
  validate      Validate CoDD frontmatter and dependency references.
  verify        Run build + test verification and trace failures to...
